author: James Dator
title: Dude Perfect's pool trick-shot video will make you feel so inadequate at the bar
text: Rec The folks from Dude Perfect are back with a new video that’s going to make you feel utterly inadequate the next time you pick up a cue in your local bar. The star of this video is Florian “Venom” Kohler, a French legend when it comes to trick-shot pool. All the shots are incredible, like every Dude Perfect video — but some of these are out of this world. Breaking clay pigeons covering crotches. Popping the ball up and shooting it off a balcony into a golf hole. But perhaps most jaw-dropping is jumping a ball over two tables and sinking six balls shaped in a butterfly. This is all so good. After the trick-shot extravaganza, Kohler hung around and played a game of pool like it was air hockey. This is very excellent. Next Up In ##Lookit
